<div id='gazette_story'>
    <div align='center'>
        <font size='4'><b>The Fashion Scene Heats Up!</b></font><br>
                                <img src='http://graphics.millsberry.com/site_gfx/interiors/gazette/gazette_20100527.png' border='1' width='280' height='200'>
                        </div>
        <div id='gazette_byline'><em>By Audrey Smythe-Wei<br>Editor-in-Chief</em></div>
        <b>Thursday, May 27, 2010</b> &mdash;
    Just when you thought Wearhouse boutique owner Loretta Rivers was going to put her sketches and sewing machine to rest...she&#039;s back at it again! And this time, she&#039;s got <a href="http://millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=1"> everything</a> you need for one cool summer in the sun. <br><br>Plus, the new duds include Millsberry&#039;s most-wanted. That&#039;s right---new <a href="http://millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=1">bathing suits</a>! You asked for them and now you&#039;ve got &#039;em! <br><br>We stopped by the Millsberry <a href="http://millsberry.com/communitycenter/pool.phtml">Pool</a> to get the full scoop---and the scoop we found! It seemed as if we&#039;d stepped into the pages of a summer swim catalog! <br><br>Looking around the pool&#039;s perimeter and taking in the sea of red, <a href="http://millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=1">polka-dot bathing suits</a>, one Golden Valley resident commented: &quot;I should have known everyone would be wearing the same new suits!&quot; Smiling, she added &quot;Thankfully, Loretta also designed a <a href="http://millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=1">plaid, retro suit</a> to mix things up a bit!&quot;<br>
<br>
And for the guys? There were some new <a href="http://millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=1">swimsuits</a> in the mix for them as well--plus <a href="http://millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=1">tank tops</a> with pockets, fun plaid <a href="http://millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=1">hats</a>, <a href="http://millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=1">sunglasses</a>, and <a href="http://millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=1">more</a>!<br><br>Dojo owner, Siobhan Hidaka, was enjoying the scene. &quot;I just love this weather!&quot; he said. &quot;It gives me an excuse to cruise around on my new <a href="http://millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=7">beach-cruiser bike</a>! You know, a thick-framed bike that comes in bright, hot colors? With streamers, a horn, and a big basket to fill with flying discs, snacks, and other must-haves for a perfect June picnic! I can throw my new <a href="http://millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=1">straw beach bag</a> in there too!&quot;<br><br>Yep, the sights of summer are everywhere: awesome colors, fun clothing and patterns, and...<a href="http://millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=3">beach chairs</a>! Did we forget to mention those?! Plus, like Siobhan said, warm weather always offers a good excuse to go outside and get active. Like taking your new beach-cruiser bike for a spin around downtown Millsberry! Biking is also a great way to get some exercise and explore new places a little quicker than on foot. Also, bike riding is something you can do alone...while still feeling the warm summer sun!<br><br>So stock up on these <a href="http://millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=1">goods</a> for the summer season ahead--and cherish each warm day!<br>
    </div>

